			<sentence id="1.9">mod_auth_ldap module.  Is there someone there I can correspond with to see if </sentence>
			<sentence id="1.10">it is possible to offer Apache money to expedite the repair of the </sentence>
			<sentence id="1.11">mod_auth_ldap module?</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">This has been a known issue for some time, as the bug list can attest too.</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.2">It 
seems like a simple fix and recompile of the .</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.3">so binary files.</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.4">Can someone 
respond to this???</sentence>
